    "en": {
      "title": "President's visit to Dalatha Palace",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe visited Kandy's historic Talatha House this morning (30) and engaged in religious activities.",
        "On his visit to Dalatha Palace, the President was welcomed by Kandy Mayor Kesara Senanayake and ministers and escorted to the main entrance of Dalatha Palace.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe was welcomed by Thiavadana Nilame Pradeep Nilanga Thela and Basnayake Nilamemar of the Four Great Churches.",
        "After that, the President went to the upper floor where the Holy Tantadatu is enshrined in the Dalatha House, where he offered floral tributes, performed religious services and received the blessings of the Maha Sangha.",
        "After participating in the religious services, President Ranil went to the space reserved for special guests in the Talatha House and left a memorial note.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe is scheduled to meet Malwattu-Askiri Mahanayake Theras this afternoon."
      ],
